review:
Only thing bad is camera quality. Worst image processing device. Speed is good. Charging is ok.. heats up normally. Not more or less . Backup is ok but not best.
50MP cam for a large file jpeg with 8k resolution size, but the pixel quality sucks.
ONLY BUY IF YOU DONT USE CAMERA MUCH OR DONT BOTHER ABOUT CLEAR RICH IMAGES SHOT FROM THIS PHONE
